---
// Componente About - Marketplace para cubanos
---

<section class="bg-white py-24 px-6 border-b border-gray-100">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-sea-glass mb-6 block">
          Conectando Cubanos
        </span>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-5xl mb-8 leading-tight italic font-bold text-primary">
          El puente entre La Habana y el mundo.
        </h3>
        <div class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-8 font-serif italic space-y-4">
          <p>
            <span class="font-bold not-italic text-primary">Mambbu</span> es el marketplace donde particulares
            y agencias publican propiedades en Cuba. Sin intermediarios innecesarios, sin comisiones ocultas.
          </p>
          <p>
            Creado para <span class="text-sea-glass font-bold not-italic">cubanos en Cuba</span>
            que buscan vender, y para la
            <span class="text-sea-glass font-bold not-italic"
              >diáspora en Miami, España y México</span
            >
            que quiere invertir en la isla.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base not-italic text-gray-600 border-l-4 border-sea-glass pl-4">
            Publicar es gratis. Conectar es simple. El futuro inmobiliario de Cuba empieza aquí.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <button
            class="bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs hover:bg-sea-glass hover:text-primary transition-all border-2 border-primary hover:border-sea-glass"
          >
            Publica Gratis
          </button>
          <button
            class="bg-white text-primary px-8 py-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs hover:bg-sea-glass hover:text-white hover:border-sea-glass transition-all border-2 border-primary"
          >
            Cómo Funciona
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tarjetas de ubicaciones con imágenes y gradientes -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <!-- Cuba -->
        <div class="relative h-48 postcard-border overflow-hidden group cursor-pointer">
          <img
            src="/images/hero-havana.jpg"
            alt="La Habana"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-cuba-red/80 via-primary/60 to-primary/80 group-hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-end p-6 text-white">
            <div class="font-serif text-2xl italic font-bold mb-1">La Habana</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/90">Donde todo comienza</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Miami -->
        <div class="relative h-48 postcard-border overflow-hidden group cursor-pointer">
          <img
            src="/images/property-1.jpg"
            alt="Miami"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600/80 via-cuba-red/60 to-cuba-red/80 group-hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-end p-6 text-white">
            <div class="font-serif text-2xl italic font-bold mb-1">Miami</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/90">Nuestra familia allá</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- España -->
        <div class="relative h-48 postcard-border overflow-hidden group cursor-pointer">
          <img
            src="/images/property-2.jpg"
            alt="España"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-600/80 via-yellow-500/60 to-red-600/80 group-hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-end p-6 text-white">
            <div class="font-serif text-2xl italic font-bold mb-1">España</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/90">Conectando raíces</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- México -->
        <div class="relative h-48 postcard-border overflow-hidden group cursor-pointer">
          <img
            src="/images/property-3.jpg"
            alt="México"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-700/80 via-white/40 to-red-600/80 group-hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-end p-6 text-white">
            <div class="font-serif text-2xl italic font-bold mb-1">México</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/90">Puente al Caribe</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
